its for fully automated workflows\"]','[\"自动批准所有代码修改，无需提示确认\", \"常与 --auto-commits 搭配使用以实现完全自动化的工作流\"]','[\"All file modifications are applied immediately without review\", \"Combined with git auto-commit, changes go directly to the repository\"]','[\"所有文件修改将立即应用，无法事先审查\", \"与 git 自动提交结合使用时，修改将直接提交到代码仓库\"]','https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html','Verified against official Aider configuration documentation.',NULL,'2026-05-28','2026-06-08 11:25:43','2026-06-08 11:25:43'),(41,4,'drop','/drop','slash','Session','low','official','Remove files from the chat session to free up context space','从当前上下文中移除所有文件。','/drop',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/usage/commands.html','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:25:43','2026-06-08 11:34:07'),(42,4,'help','/help','slash','Session','low','official','show this help message and exit Aliases:','显示可用命令及使用说明。','aider --help',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--help','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:25:43','2026-06-08 11:34:07'),(43,4,'tokens','/tokens','slash','Session','low','official','Report on the number of tokens used by the current chat context','显示当前会话的令牌使用统计信息。','/tokens',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/usage/commands.html','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:25:43','2026-06-08 11:34:07'),(44,4,'system-md','.aider.system.md','config','Config','low','official','Custom system prompt file loaded at session start.','会话启动时加载的自定义系统提示词文件。','.aider.system.md',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-28','2026-06-08 11:25:43','2026-06-08 11:25:43'),(45,4,'conf-yml','.aider.conf.yml','config','Config','low','official','YAML configuration file for persistent Aider settings.','用于持久化 Aider 设置的 YAML 配置文件。','.aider.conf.yml',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aid