改，而非运行对话（debug）','aider --apply FILE','FILE',NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_APPLY\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--apply-file','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:42'),(142,4,'apply-clipboard-edits','--apply-clipboard-edits','flag','Session','low','official','Apply clipboard contents as edits using the main model’s editor format Default: False','使用主 model 的编辑器格式将剪贴板内容作为编辑内容应用 默认值：False','aider --apply-clipboard-edits',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_APPLY_CLIPBOARD_EDITS\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--apply-clipboard-edits','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:42'),(143,4,'exit','--exit','flag','Session','low','official','Do all startup activities then exit before accepting user input (debug) Default: False','完成所有启动操作后，在接受用户输入之前退出（debug 用途）默认值：False','aider --exit',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_EXIT\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--exit','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:43'),(144,4,'show-repo-map','--show-repo-map','flag','Session','low','official','Print the repo map and exit (debug) Default: False','打印 repo map 并退出（debug 模式） 默认值：False','aider --show-repo-map',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_SHOW_REPO_MAP\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--show-repo-map','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:43'),(145,4,'show-prompts','--show-prompts','flag','Session','low','official','Print the system prompts and exit (debug) Default: False','打印系统 prompt 并退出（debug 模式） 默认值：False','aider --show-prompts',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_SHOW_PROMPTS\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--show-prompts','Scraped from of