dd URLs to chat (default: True) Default: True  Aliases:','启用/禁用 URL 检测及将 URL 添加到对话的提示功能（默认：True）默认值：True  别名：','aider --detect-urls',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_DETECT_URLS\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--detect-urls','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:43'),(168,4,'editor','--editor','option','Config','low','official','Specify which editor to use for the /editor command','指定用于 /editor 命令的编辑器','aider --editor VALUE','VALUE',NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_EDITOR\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--editor-value','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:43'),(169,4,'shell-completions','--shell-completions','option','Config','low','official','Print shell completion script for the specified SHELL and exit. Supported shells: bash, tcsh, zsh. Example: aider –shell-completions bash','为指定的 SHELL 打印 shell 补全脚本并退出。支持的 shell：bash、tcsh、zsh。示例：aider --shell-completions bash','aider --shell-completions SHELL','SHELL',NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_SHELL_COMPLETIONS\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--shell-completions-shell','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:43'),(170,4,'opus','--opus','flag','Config','low','official','Use claude-3-opus-20240229 model for the main chat (deprecated, use –model) Default: False','使用 claude-3-opus-20240229 model 进行主对话（已弃用，请使用 –model）默认值：False','aider --opus',NULL,NULL,NULL,'[\"Environment variable: AIDER_OPUS\"]',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://aider.chat/docs/config/options.html#--opus','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:34:08','2026-06-08 11:45:43'),(171,4,'sonnet','--sonnet','flag','Config','low','official','Use anthropic/claude-3-7-sonnet-20250219 model for the main chat (deprecated, use –model) Default: False