documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(689,2,'project-doc-fallback-filenames','project_doc_fallback_filenames','config','Config','low','official','Additional filenames to try when AGENTS.md is missing.','当 AGENTS.md 缺失时依次尝试的备用文件名列表。','project_doc_fallback_filenames = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(690,2,'project-doc-max-bytes','project_doc_max_bytes','config','Config','low','official','Maximum bytes read from AGENTS.md when building project instructions.','构建项目指令时从 AGENTS.md 读取的最大字节数。','project_doc_max_bytes = number','number',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(691,2,'project-root-markers','project_root_markers','config','Config','low','official','List of project root marker filenames; used when searching parent directories for the project root.','项目根目录标记文件名列表；向上遍历父目录以定位项目根目录时使用。','project_root_markers = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(692,2,'projects-<path>-trust-level','projects.<path>.trust_level','config','Config','high','official','Mark a project or worktree as trusted or untrusted (\"trusted\" | \"untrusted\"). Untrusted projects skip project-scoped .codex/ layers, including project-local config, hooks, and rules.','将项目或 worktree 标记为受信任或不受信任（\"trusted\" | \"untrusted\"）。不受信任的项目将跳过项目级 .codex/ 层，包括项目本地的 config、hooks 及规则。','projects.<path>.trust_level = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(693,2,'review-model','review_model','config','Model','low','official','Optional model override used by /review (defaults to the current session model).','供 /review 使用的可选 model 覆盖项（默认使用当前 session 的 model）。','review_model = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(694,2,'sandbox-mode','sandbox_mode','config','Permission','medium','official','Sandbox policy for filesystem and network access during command execution.','命令执行期间文件系统与网络访问的 sandbox 策略。','sandbox_mode = read-only | workspace-write | danger-full-access','read-only | workspace-write | danger-full-access',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(695,2,'sandbox-workspace-write-exclude-slash-tmp','sandbox_workspace_write.exclude_slash_tmp','config','Permission','medium','official','Exclude /tmp from writable roots in workspace-write mode.','在 workspace-write 模式下，将 /tmp 从可写根目录中排除。','sandbox_workspace_write.exclude_slash_tmp = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(696,2,'sandbox-workspace-write-exclude-tmpdir-env-var','sandbox_workspace_write.exclude_tmpdir_env_var','config','Permission','medium','official','Exclude $TMPDIR from writable roots in workspace-write mode.','在 workspace-write 模式下，将 $TMPDIR 从可写根目录中排除。','sandbox_workspace_write.exclude_tmpdir_env_var = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(697,2,'sandbox-workspace-write-network-access','sandbox_workspace_write.network_access','config','Permission','medium','official','Allow outbound network access inside the workspace-write sandbox.','允许在 workspace-write sandbox 内发起出站网络访问。','sandbox_workspace_write.network_access = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(698,2,'sandbox-workspace-write-writable-roots','sandbox_workspace_write.writable_roots','config','Permission','medium','official','Additional writable roots when sandbox_mode = \"workspace-write\".','当 sandbox_mode = \"workspace-write\" 时，附加的可写根目录。','sandbox_workspace_write.writable_roots = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(699,2,'service-tier','service_tier','config','Config','low','official','Preferred service tier for new turns. Built-in values include flex and fast; legacy fast config maps to the request value priority, and catalog-provided tier IDs can also be stored.','新轮次的首选服务层级。内置值包括 flex 和 fast；旧版 fast config 映射为请求值 priority，也可存储目录提供的层级 ID。','service_tier = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(700,2,'shell-environment-policy-exclude','shell_environment_policy.exclude','config','Config','low','official','Glob patterns for removing environment variables after the defaults.','在默认值之后用于移除环境变量的 Glob 模式。','shell_environment_policy.exclude = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(701,2,'shell-environment-policy-experimental-use-profile','shell_environment_policy.experimental_use_profile','config','Config','low','official','Use the user shell profile when spawning subprocesses.','在生成子进程时使用用户 shell 配置文件。','shell_environment_policy.experimental_use_profile = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(702,2,'shell-environment-policy-ignore-default-excludes','shell_environment_policy.ignore_default_excludes','config','Config','low','official','Keep variables containing KEY/SECRET/TOKEN before other filters run.','在其他过滤器运行之前，保留名称中包含 KEY/SECRET/TOKEN 的变量。','shell_environment_policy.ignore_default_excludes = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(703,2,'shell-environment-policy-include-only','shell_environment_policy.include_only','config','Config','low','official','Whitelist of patterns; when set only matching variables are kept.','模式白名单；设置后仅保留与之匹配的变量。','shell_environment_policy.include_only = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(704,2,'shell-environment-policy-inherit','shell_environment_policy.inherit','config','Config','low','official','Baseline environment inheritance when spawning subprocesses.','生成子进程时的基准环境继承策略。','shell_environment_policy.inherit = all | core | none','all | core | none',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(705,2,'shell-environment-policy-set','shell_environment_policy.set','config','Config','low','official','Explicit environment overrides injected into every subprocess.','注入到每个子进程的显式环境覆盖项。','shell_environment_policy.set = map<string,string>','map<string,string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(706,2,'show-raw-agent-reasoning','show_raw_agent_reasoning','config','Model','low','official','Surface raw reasoning content when the active model emits it.','当活跃 model 输出原始推理内容时将其展示出来。','show_raw_agent_reasoning = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(707,2,'skills-config','skills.config','config','Config','low','official','Per-skill enablement overrides stored in config.toml.','存储在 config.toml 中的每个 skill 的启用覆盖配置。','skills.config = array<object>','array<object>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(708,2,'skills-config-<index>-enabled','skills.config.<index>.enabled','config','Config','low','official','Enable or disable the referenced skill.','启用或禁用指定的 skill。','skills.config.<index>.enabled = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(709,2,'skills-config-<index>-path','skills.config.<index>.path','config','Config','low','official','Path to a skill folder containing SKILL.md.','包含 SKILL.md 的 skill 文件夹路径。','skills.config.<index>.path = string (path)','string (path)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(710,2,'sqlite-home','sqlite_home','config','Config','low','official','Directory where Codex stores the SQLite-backed state DB used by agent jobs and other resumable runtime state.','Codex 存储 SQLite 状态数据库的目录，供 agent 任务及其他可恢复的运行时状态使用。','sqlite_home = string (path)','string (path)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(711,2,'suppress-unstable-features-warning','suppress_unstable_features_warning','config','Config','low','official','Suppress the warning that appears when under-development feature flags are enabled.','抑制启用开发中功能 flag 时出现的警告提示。','suppress_unstable_features_warning = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(712,2,'tool-output-token-limit','tool_output_token_limit','config','MCP','low','official','Token budget for storing individual tool/function outputs in history.','用于在历史记录中存储单个 tool/function 输出的 token 预算。','tool_output_token_limit = number','number',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(713,2,'tool-suggest-disabled-tools','tool_suggest.disabled_tools','config','MCP','low','official','Disable suggestions for specific discoverable connectors or plugins. Each entry uses type = \"connector\" or \"plugin\" and an id.','禁用特定可发现 connector 或 plugin 的建议。每个条目使用 type = \"connector\" 或 \"plugin\" 及对应的 id。','tool_suggest.disabled_tools = array<table>','array<table>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(714,2,'tool-suggest-discoverables','tool_suggest.discoverables','config','MCP','low','official','Allow tool suggestions for additional discoverable connectors or plugins. Each entry uses type = \"connector\" or \"plugin\" and an id.','允许对额外可发现 connector 或 plugin 提供 tool 建议。每个条目使用 type = \"connector\" 或 \"plugin\" 及对应的 id。','tool_suggest.discoverables = array<table>','array<table>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(715,2,'tools-view-image','tools.view_image','config','MCP','low','official','Enable the local-image attachment tool view_image.','启用本地图片附件 tool view_image。','tools.view_image = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(716,2,'tools-web-search','tools.web_search','config','MCP','low','official','Optional web search tool configuration. The legacy boolean form is still accepted, but the object form lets you set search context size, allowed domains, and approximate user location.','可选的网络搜索 tool 配置。仍接受旧版布尔值形式，但对象形式允许设置搜索 context 大小、允许的域名及大致用户位置。','tools.web_search = boolean | { context_size = \"low|medium|high\", allowed_domains = [string], location = { country, region, city, timezone } }','boolean | { context_size = \"low|medium|high\", allowed_domains = [string], location = { country, region, city, timezone } }',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(717,2,'tui','tui','config','Config','low','official','TUI-specific options such as enabling inline desktop notifications.','TUI 专属选项，例如启用内联桌面通知。','tui = table','table',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(718,2,'tui-alternate-screen','tui.alternate_screen','config','Config','high','official','Control alternate screen usage for the TUI (default: auto; auto skips it in Zellij to preserve scrollback).','控制 TUI 的备用屏幕使用方式（默认值：auto；在 Zellij 中 auto 会跳过以保留滚动历史）。','tui.alternate_screen = auto | always | never','auto | always | never',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(719,2,'tui-animations','tui.animations','config','Config','low','official','Enable terminal animations (welcome screen, shimmer, spinner) (default: true).','启用终端动画（欢迎屏幕、shimmer、spinner）（默认值：true）。','tui.animations = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(720,2,'tui-keymap-<context>-<action>','tui.keymap.<context>.<action>','config','Permission','medium','official','Keyboard shortcut binding for a TUI action. Supported contexts include global, chat, composer, editor, vim_normal, vim_operator, vim_text_object, pager, list, and approval. Selected composer actions fall back to matching tui.keymap.global bindings; context-specific bindings take precedence when supported.','TUI 动作的键盘快捷键绑定。支持的 context 包括 global、chat、composer、editor、vim_normal、vim_operator、vim_text_object、pager、list 和 approval。部分 composer 动作会回退至匹配的 tui.keymap.global 绑定；在支持的情况下，特定 context 的绑定优先级更高。','tui.keymap.<context>.<action> = string | array<string>','string | array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(721,2,'tui-keymap-<context>-<action> = []','tui.keymap.<context>.<action> = []','config','Config','low','official','Unbind the action in that keymap context. Key names use normalized strings such as ctrl-a, shift-enter, page-down, or minus.','在该 keymap context 中解除绑定该动作。键名使用规范化字符串，例如 ctrl-a、shift-enter、page-down 或 minus。','tui.keymap.<context>.<action> = [] = empty array','empty array',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(722,2,'tui-model-availability-nux-<model>','tui.model_availability_nux.<model>','config','Model','low','official','Internal startup-tooltip state keyed by model slug.','以 model slug 为键的内部启动 tooltip 状态。','tui.model_availability_nux.<model> = integer','integer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(723,2,'tui-notification-condition','tui.notification_condition','config','Config','low','official','Control whether TUI notifications fire only when the terminal is unfocused or regardless of focus. Defaults to unfocused.','控制 TUI 通知的触发条件：仅在终端失去焦点时触发，或无论焦点状态均触发。默认为失去焦点时触发。','tui.notification_condition = unfocused | always','unfocused | always',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(724,2,'tui-notification-method','tui.notification_method','config','Config','medium','official','Notification method for terminal notifications (default: auto).','终端通知的通知方式（默认值：auto）。','tui.notification_method = auto | osc9 | bel','auto | osc9 | bel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(725,2,'tui-notifications','tui.notifications','config','Config','low','official','Enable TUI notifications; optionally restrict to specific event types.','启用 TUI 通知；可选择限定为特定事件类型。','tui.notifications = boolean | array<string>','boolean | array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(726,2,'tui-raw-output-mode','tui.raw_output_mode','config','Config','low','official','Start the TUI in raw scrollback mode for copy-friendly terminal selection (default: false). You can toggle it with /raw or the default alt-r key binding.','以原始滚动回滚模式启动 TUI，便于终端复制选择（默认值：false）。可通过 /raw 或默认快捷键 alt-r 切换该模式。','tui.raw_output_mode = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(727,2,'tui-show-tooltips','tui.show_tooltips','config','MCP','low','official','Show onboarding tooltips in the TUI welcome screen (default: true).','在 TUI 欢迎页面显示引导 tooltip（默认值：true）。','tui.show_tooltips = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(728,2,'tui-status-line','tui.status_line','config','Config','low','official','Ordered list of TUI footer status-line item identifiers. null disables the status line.','TUI 底部状态栏条目标识符的有序列表。设为 null 可禁用状态栏。','tui.status_line = array<string> | null','array<string> | null',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(729,2,'tui-terminal-title','tui.terminal_title','config','Config','low','official','Ordered list of terminal window/tab title item identifiers. Defaults to [\"spinner\", \"project\"]; null disables title updates.','终端窗口/标签页标题条目标识符的有序列表。默认值为 [\"spinner\", \"project\"]；设为 null 可禁用标题更新。','tui.terminal_title = array<string> | null','array<string> | null',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(730,2,'tui-theme','tui.theme','config','Config','low','official','Syntax-highlighting theme override (kebab-case theme name).','语法高亮主题覆盖项（使用 kebab-case 格式的主题名称）。','tui.theme = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(731,2,'tui-vim-mode-default','tui.vim_mode_default','config','Session','low','official','Start the composer in Vim normal mode instead of insert mode (default: false). You can still toggle it per session with /vim.',NULL,'tui.vim_mode_default = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 11:37:50'),(732,2,'web-search','web_search','config','Permission','high','official','Web search mode (default: \"cached\"; cached uses an OpenAI-maintained index and does not fetch live pages; if you use --yolo or another full access sandbox setting, it defaults to \"live\"). Use \"live\" to fetch the most recent data from the web, or \"disabled\" to remove the tool.','Web 搜索模式（默认值：\"cached\"；cached 使用 OpenAI 维护的索引，不抓取实时页面；若使用 --yolo 或其他完全访问 sandbox 设置，则默认为 \"live\"）。使用 \"live\" 获取最新网络数据，或使用 \"disabled\" 移除该工具。','web_search = disabled | cached | live','disabled | cached | live',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(733,2,'windows-wsl-setup-acknowledged','windows_wsl_setup_acknowledged','config','Config','low','official','Track Windows onboarding acknowledgement (Windows only).','跟踪 Windows 引导确认状态（仅限 Windows）。','windows_wsl_setup_acknowledged = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(734,2,'windows-sandbox','windows.sandbox','config','Permission','medium','official','Windows-only native sandbox mode when running Codex natively on Windows.','在 Windows 上原生运行 Codex 时使用的仅限 Windows 的原生 sandbox 模式。','windows.sandbox = unelevated | elevated','unelevated | elevated',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(735,2,'windows-sandbox-private-desktop','windows.sandbox_private_desktop','config','Permission','medium','official','Run the final sandboxed child process on a private desktop by default on native Windows. Set false only for compatibility with the older Winsta0\\\\Default behavior.','在原生 Windows 上默认将最终 sandbox 子进程运行于私有桌面。仅在需要兼容旧版 Winsta0\\\\Default 行为时设为 false。','windows.sandbox_private_desktop = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(736,2,'allow-managed-hooks-only','allow_managed_hooks_only','config','Session','high','official','When true, Codex skips user, project, session, and plugin hooks while still allowing managed hooks from requirements.toml and other managed config layers.','为 true 时，Codex 跳过用户、项目、session 和 plugin hooks，但仍允许来自 requirements.toml 及其他托管 config 层的 managed hooks。','allow_managed_hooks_only = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(737,2,'allowed-approval-policies','allowed_approval_policies','config','Permission','medium','official','Allowed values for approval_policy (for example untrusted, on-request, never, and granular).','approval_policy 的允许值（例如 untrusted、on-request、never 和 granular）。','allowed_approval_policies = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(738,2,'allowed-approvals-reviewers','allowed_approvals_reviewers','config','Permission','medium','official','Allowed values for approvals_reviewer, such as user and auto_review.','approvals_reviewer 的允许值，例如 user 和 auto_review。','allowed_approvals_reviewers = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(739,2,'allowed-sandbox-modes','allowed_sandbox_modes','config','Permission','medium','official','Allowed values for sandbox_mode.','sandbox_mode 的允许值。','allowed_sandbox_modes = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(740,2,'allowed-web-search-modes','allowed_web_search_modes','config','Config','low','official','Allowed values for web_search (disabled, cached, live). disabled is always allowed; an empty list effectively allows only disabled.','web_search 的允许值（disabled、cached、live）。disabled 始终被允许；空列表实际上仅允许 disabled。','allowed_web_search_modes = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(741,2,'experimental-network','experimental_network','config','Permission','medium','official','Network access requirements enforced from requirements.toml. These constraints are separate from features.network_proxy and can configure sandboxed networking without the user feature flag.','由 requirements.toml 强制执行的网络访问要求。这些约束独立于 features.network_proxy，可在不使用用户 feature flag 的情况下配置 sandbox 网络。','experimental_network = table','table',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(742,2,'experimental-network-allow-local-binding','experimental_network.allow_local_binding','config','Permission','medium','official','Permit broader local/private-network access for sandboxed networking. Exact local IP literal or localhost allow rules can still permit specific local targets when this stays false.','为 sandbox 网络允许更广泛的本地/私有网络访问。当此项为 false 时，精确的本地 IP 字面量或 localhost 允许规则仍可放行特定本地目标。','experimental_network.allow_local_binding = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(743,2,'experimental-network-allow-upstream-proxy','experimental_network.allow_upstream_proxy','config','Permission','medium','official','Allow sandboxed networking to chain through an upstream proxy from the environment.','允许 sandbox 网络通过环境中的上游 proxy 进行链式访问。','experimental_network.allow_upstream_proxy = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(744,2,'experimental-network-allowed-domains','experimental_network.allowed_domains','config','Permission','medium','official','List-shaped administrator allow rules for sandboxed networking. Do not combine this with experimental_network.domains.','用于 sandbox 网络的列表形式管理员允许规则。请勿与 experimental_network.domains 同时使用。','experimental_network.allowed_domains = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(745,2,'experimental-network-dangerously-allow-all-unix-sockets','experimental_network.dangerously_allow_all_unix_sockets','config','Config','high','official','Permit arbitrary Unix socket destinations instead of allowlist-only access. Use only in tightly controlled environments.','允许任意 Unix socket 目标，而非仅限白名单访问。仅在严格受控的环境中使用。','experimental_network.dangerously_allow_all_unix_sockets = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(746,2,'experimental-network-dangerously-allow-non-loopback-proxy','experimental_network.dangerously_allow_non_loopback_proxy','config','Config','high','official','Permit non-loopback listener addresses for [experimental_network] requirements. Enabling it can expose listeners beyond localhost.','允许 [experimental_network] 使用非回环监听地址。启用后可能使监听器暴露在 localhost 之外。','experimental_network.dangerously_allow_non_loopback_proxy = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(747,2,'experimental-network-denied-domains','experimental_network.denied_domains','config','Permission','medium','official','List-shaped administrator deny rules for sandboxed networking. Do not combine this with experimental_network.domains.','用于 sandbox 网络的列表型管理员拒绝规则。请勿与 experimental_network.domains 同时使用。','experimental_network.denied_domains = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(748,2,'experimental-network-domains','experimental_network.domains','config','Permission','medium','official','Map-shaped administrator domain policy for sandboxed networking. Supports exact hosts, *.example.com for subdomains only, **.example.com for apex plus subdomains, and global * allow rules; prefer scoped rules because * broadly opens public outbound access. deny wins on conflicts. Do not combine this with experimental_network.allowed_domains or experimental_network.denied_domains.','用于 sandbox 网络的映射型管理员域名策略。支持精确主机名、*.example.com（仅匹配子域名）、**.example.com（匹配顶级域名及子域名），以及全局 * 放行规则；建议使用精确规则，因为 * 会广泛开放公网出站访问。冲突时 deny 优先。请勿与 experimental_network.allowed_domains 或 experimental_network.denied_domains 同时使用。','experimental_network.domains = map<string, allow | deny>','map<string, allow | deny>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(749,2,'experimental-network-enabled','experimental_network.enabled','config','Permission','medium','official','Enable sandboxed networking requirements. This does not grant network access when the active sandbox keeps command networking off.','启用 sandbox 网络功能。若当前 sandbox 已关闭命令的网络访问，此选项不会授予网络访问权限。','experimental_network.enabled = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(750,2,'experimental-network-http-port','experimental_network.http_port','config','Config','low','official','Loopback HTTP listener port to use for [experimental_network] requirements.','[experimental_network] 所使用的回环 HTTP 监听端口。','experimental_network.http_port = integer','integer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(751,2,'experimental-network-managed-allowed-domains-only','experimental_network.managed_allowed_domains_only','config','Permission','medium','official','When true, only administrator-managed allow rules remain effective while sandboxed networking requirements are active; user allowlist additions are ignored. Without managed allow rules, user-added domain allow rules do not remain effective.','为 true 时，sandbox 网络功能激活期间仅管理员托管的允许规则生效，用户添加的白名单条目将被忽略。若不存在管理员托管的允许规则，用户添加的域名允许规则同样不生效。','experimental_network.managed_allowed_domains_only = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(752,2,'experimental-network-socks-port','experimental_network.socks_port','config','Config','low','official','Loopback SOCKS5 listener port to use for [experimental_network] requirements.','[experimental_network] 所使用的回环 SOCKS5 监听端口。','experimental_network.socks_port = integer','integer',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(753,2,'experimental-network-unix-sockets','experimental_network.unix_sockets','config','Permission','medium','official','Administrator-managed Unix socket policy for sandboxed networking.','用于 sandbox 网络的管理员托管 Unix socket 策略。','experimental_network.unix_sockets = map<string, allow | deny>','map<string, allow | deny>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(754,2,'features','features','config','Config','low','official','Pinned feature values keyed by the canonical names from config.toml\'s [features] table.','以 config.toml 中 [features] 表的规范名称为键的固定功能值。','features = table','table',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(755,2,'features-browser-use','features.browser_use','config','Config','low','official','Set to false in requirements.toml to disable Browser Use and Browser Agent availability.','在 requirements.toml 中设置为 false 可禁用 Browser Use 和 Browser Agent 的可用性。','features.browser_use = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(756,2,'features-computer-use','features.computer_use','config','Config','low','official','Set to false in requirements.toml to disable Computer Use availability and related install or enablement flows.','在 requirements.toml 中设置为 false 可禁用 Computer Use 的可用性及相关安装或启用流程。','features.computer_use = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(757,2,'features-in-app-browser','features.in_app_browser','config','Config','low','official','Set to false in requirements.toml to disable the in-app browser pane.','在 requirements.toml 中设置为 false 以禁用应用内浏览器面板。','features.in_app_browser = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(758,2,'guardian-policy-config','guardian_policy_config','config','Config','medium','official','Managed Markdown policy instructions for automatic review. This takes precedence over local [auto_review].policy. Blank values are ignored.','用于自动审查的托管 Markdown 策略指令。优先级高于本地 [auto_review].policy 配置，空值将被忽略。','guardian_policy_config = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(759,2,'hooks-managed-dir','hooks.managed_dir','config','Config','low','official','Directory containing managed hook scripts on macOS and Linux. Codex validates that it is absolute and exists before loading managed hooks.','macOS 和 Linux 上托管 hook 脚本所在目录。Codex 在加载托管 hook 前会验证该路径为绝对路径且目录存在。','hooks.managed_dir = string (absolute path)','string (absolute path)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(760,2,'hooks-windows-managed-dir','hooks.windows_managed_dir','config','Config','low','official','Directory containing managed hook scripts on Windows. Codex validates that it is absolute and exists before loading managed hooks.','Windows 上托管 hook 脚本所在目录。Codex 在加载托管 hook 前会验证该路径为绝对路径且目录存在。','hooks.windows_managed_dir = string (absolute path)','string (absolute path)',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(761,2,'mcp-servers','mcp_servers','config','MCP','low','official','Allowlist of MCP servers that may be enabled. Both the server name (<id>) and its identity must match for the MCP server to be enabled. Any configured MCP server not in the allowlist (or with a mismatched identity) is disabled.','允许启用的 MCP server 白名单。server 名称（<id>）及其身份标识必须同时匹配，该 MCP server 才会被启用。不在白名单中或身份标识不匹配的已配置 MCP server 将被禁用。','mcp_servers = table','table',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(762,2,'mcp-servers-<id>-identity','mcp_servers.<id>.identity','config','MCP','low','official','Identity rule for a single MCP server. Set either command (stdio) or url (streamable HTTP).','单个 MCP server 的身份规则。设置 command（stdio）或 url（streamable HTTP）其中之一。','mcp_servers.<id>.identity = table','table',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(763,2,'mcp-servers-<id>-identity-command','mcp_servers.<id>.identity.command','config','MCP','low','official','Allow an MCP stdio server when its mcp_servers.<id>.command matches this command.','当 MCP stdio 服务器的 mcp_servers.<id>.command 与此命令匹配时，允许该服务器。','mcp_servers.<id>.identity.command = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(764,2,'mcp-servers-<id>-identity-url','mcp_servers.<id>.identity.url','config','MCP','low','official','Allow an MCP streamable HTTP server when its mcp_servers.<id>.url matches this URL.','当 MCP 可流式 HTTP 服务器的 mcp_servers.<id>.url 与此 URL 匹配时，允许该服务器。','mcp_servers.<id>.identity.url = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:10'),(765,2,'permissions-filesystem-deny-read','permissions.filesystem.deny_read','config','Permission','low','official','Admin-enforced filesystem read denials. Entries can be paths or glob patterns, and users cannot weaken them with local config.','管理员强制执行的文件系统读取拒绝规则。条目可以是路径或 glob 模式，用户无法通过本地 config 削弱这些限制。','permissions.filesystem.deny_read = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(766,2,'plugin-sharing','plugin_sharing','config','Config','low','official','Set to false in cloud-managed requirements.toml to disable workspace sharing for locally built plugins.','在云端管理的 requirements.toml 中设置为 false，可禁用本地构建插件的工作区共享功能。','plugin_sharing = boolean','boolean',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(767,2,'remote-sandbox-config','remote_sandbox_config','config','Permission','medium','official','Host-specific sandbox requirements. The first entry whose hostname_patterns match the resolved host name overrides top-level allowed_sandbox_modes for that requirements source. Host-specific entries currently override sandbox modes only.','特定主机的 sandbox 要求。第一个 hostname_patterns 与已解析主机名匹配的条目，将覆盖该要求来源的顶层 allowed_sandbox_modes。当前，特定主机条目仅覆盖 sandbox 模式。','remote_sandbox_config = array<table>','array<table>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(768,2,'remote-sandbox-config[]-allowed-sandbox-modes','remote_sandbox_config[].allowed_sandbox_modes','config','Permission','medium','official','Allowed sandbox modes to apply when this host-specific entry matches.','当此特定主机条目匹配时所应用的允许 sandbox 模式。','remote_sandbox_config[].allowed_sandbox_modes = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(769,2,'remote-sandbox-config[]-hostname-patterns','remote_sandbox_config[].hostname_patterns','config','Permission','medium','official','Case-insensitive host name patterns. Supports * for any sequence of characters and ? for one character.','不区分大小写的主机名模式。支持 * 匹配任意字符序列，? 匹配单个字符。','remote_sandbox_config[].hostname_patterns = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(770,2,'rules','rules','config','Config','low','official','Admin-enforced command rules merged with .rules files. Requirements rules must be restrictive.','管理员强制执行的命令规则，与 .rules 文件合并生效。要求规则必须具有限制性。','rules = table','table',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(771,2,'rules-prefix-rules','rules.prefix_rules','config','Config','low','official','List of enforced prefix rules. Each rule must include pattern and decision.','强制执行的前缀规则列表。每条规则必须包含 pattern 和 decision。','rules.prefix_rules = array<table>','array<table>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(772,2,'rules-prefix-rules[]-decision','rules.prefix_rules[].decision','config','Config','low','official','Required. Requirements rules can only prompt or forbid (not allow).','必填项。要求规则只能设为 prompt 或 forbid，不可设为 allow。','rules.prefix_rules[].decision = prompt | forbidden','prompt | forbidden',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(773,2,'rules-prefix-rules[]-justification','rules.prefix_rules[].justification','config','Permission','medium','official','Optional non-empty rationale surfaced in approval prompts or rejection messages.','可选的非空理由说明，将显示在审批 prompt 或拒绝消息中。','rules.prefix_rules[].justification = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(774,2,'rules-prefix-rules[]-pattern','rules.prefix_rules[].pattern','config','Config','low','official','Command prefix expressed as pattern tokens. Each token sets either token or any_of.','以 pattern token 表示的命令前缀。每个 token 设置 token 或 any_of。','rules.prefix_rules[].pattern = array<table>','array<table>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(775,2,'rules-prefix-rules[]-pattern[]-any-of','rules.prefix_rules[].pattern[].any_of','config','Config','low','official','A list of allowed alternative tokens at this position.','此位置允许的备选 token 列表。','rules.prefix_rules[].pattern[].any_of = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(776,2,'rules-prefix-rules[]-pattern[]-token','rules.prefix_rules[].pattern[].token','config','Config','low','official','A single literal token at this position.','此位置的单个字面 token。','rules.prefix_rules[].pattern[].token = string','string',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(777,2,'windows-allowed-sandbox-implementations','windows.allowed_sandbox_implementations','config','Permission','medium','official','Allowed native Windows sandbox implementations for windows.sandbox (elevated and unelevated). The list must not be empty. When both are allowed and no mode is selected, Codex prefers elevated.','windows.sandbox 允许使用的原生 Windows sandbox 实现（elevated 与 unelevated）。列表不得为空。当两者均被允许且未指定模式时，Codex 优先选择 elevated。','windows.allowed_sandbox_implementations = array<string>','array<string>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-reference','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:11'),(778,2,'feature-apps','--enable apps','flag','Config','low','official','Enable ChatGPT Apps/connectors support','启用 ChatGPT Apps/connectors 支持。','codex --enable apps',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(779,2,'feature-codex_git_commit','--enable codex_git_commit','flag','Config','low','official','Enable Codex-generated git commits and commit attribution trailers','启用 Codex 生成的 git commit 及 commit 署名标记。','codex --enable codex_git_commit',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(780,2,'feature-hooks','--enable hooks','flag','Config','low','official','Enable lifecycle hooks from hooks.json or inline [hooks]. See Hooks.','从 hooks.json 或内联 [hooks] 启用生命周期 hooks。参见 Hooks。','codex --enable hooks',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:50','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(781,2,'feature-fast_mode','--enable fast_mode','flag','Config','low','official','Enable Fast mode selection and the service_tier = \"fast\" path','启用 Fast mode 选择及 service_tier = \"fast\" 路径。','codex --enable fast_mode',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(782,2,'feature-memories','--enable memories','flag','Config','low','official','Enable Memories','启用 Memories。','codex --enable memories',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(783,2,'feature-multi_agent','--enable multi_agent','flag','Config','low','official','Enable subagent collaboration tools','启用子代理协作工具。','codex --enable multi_agent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(784,2,'feature-personality','--enable personality','flag','Config','low','official','Enable personality selection controls','启用个性化选择控件。','codex --enable personality',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(785,2,'feature-shell_snapshot','--enable shell_snapshot','flag','Config','low','official','Snapshot your shell environment to speed up repeated commands','快照当前 shell 环境，以加速重复命令的执行。','codex --enable shell_snapshot',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(786,2,'feature-shell_tool','--enable shell_tool','flag','Config','low','official','Enable the default shell tool','启用默认 shell 工具。','codex --enable shell_tool',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(787,2,'feature-unified_exec','--enable unified_exec','flag','Config','low','official','Use the unified PTY-backed exec tool','使用基于统一 PTY 的 exec 工具','codex --enable unified_exec',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(788,2,'feature-undo','--enable undo','flag','Config','low','official','Enable undo via per-turn git ghost snapshots','通过每轮 git ghost 快照启用撤销功能','codex --enable undo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(789,2,'feature-web_search','--enable web_search','flag','Config','low','official','Legacy toggle; prefer the top-level web_search setting','旧版开关；建议使用顶层 web_search 设置','codex --enable web_search',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(790,2,'feature-web_search_cached','--enable web_search_cached','flag','Config','low','official','Legacy toggle that maps to web_search = \"cached\" when unset','旧版开关，未设置时映射为 web_search = \"cached\"','codex --enable web_search_cached',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(791,2,'feature-web_search_request','--enable web_search_request','flag','Config','low','official','Legacy toggle that maps to web_search = \"live\" when unset','旧版开关，未设置时映射为 web_search = \"live\"','codex --enable web_search_request',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://developers.openai.com/codex/config-basic','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-08','2026-06-08 11:37:51','2026-06-08 12:07:09'),(792,5,'tui','tui','subcommand','Session','low','official','Start the OpenCode terminal user interface.','启动 OpenCode 终端用户界面。','opencode tui',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(793,5,'create','create','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Create a new agent with custom configuration. This command will guide you through creating a new agent with a custom system prompt and permission configuration. Anything you don’t allow is denied in the generated agent’s frontmatter.','使用自定义配置创建新的代理。 此命令将引导您使用自定义系统提示词和工具配置来创建新的代理。','opencode create',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(794,5,'list','list','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','List all available agents.','列出所有可用的代理。','opencode list',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(795,5,'auth','auth','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Command to manage credentials and login for providers.','管理提供商的凭据和登录信息的命令。','opencode auth',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(796,5,'login','login','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','OpenCode is powered by the provider list at Models.dev, so you can use opencode auth login to configure API keys for any provider you’d like to use. This is stored in ~/.local/share/opencode/auth.json. When OpenCode starts up it loads the providers from the credentials file. And if there are any keys defined in your environments or a .env file in your project.','OpenCode 基于 Models.dev 的提供商列表运行，因此您可以使用 opencode auth login 为任何想要使用的提供商配置 API 密钥。密钥存储在 ~/.local/share/opencode/auth.json 中。 OpenCode 启动时会从凭据文件加载提供商信息，同时也会加载环境变量或项目中 .env 文件中定义的密钥。','opencode login',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(797,5,'logout','logout','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Logs you out of a provider by clearing it from the credentials file.','从凭据文件中清除提供商信息以完成登出。','opencode logout',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(798,5,'github','github','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Manage the GitHub agent for repository automation.','管理用于仓库自动化的 GitHub 代理。','opencode github',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(799,5,'install','install','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Install the GitHub agent in your repository. This sets up the necessary GitHub Actions workflow and guides you through the configuration process. Learn more.','在您的仓库中安装 GitHub 代理。 此命令会设置必要的 GitHub Actions 工作流并引导您完成配置过程。了解更多。','opencode install',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(800,5,'run','run','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Run the GitHub agent. This is typically used in GitHub Actions.','运行 GitHub 代理。通常在 GitHub Actions 中使用。','opencode run',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(801,5,'add','add','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Add an MCP server to your configuration. This command will guide you through adding either a local or remote MCP server.','将 MCP 服务器添加到您的配置中。 此命令将引导您添加本地或远程 MCP 服务器。','opencode add',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(802,5,'debug','debug','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Debug OAuth connection issues for an MCP server.','调试 MCP 服务器的 OAuth 连接问题。','opencode debug',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(803,5,'serve','serve','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Start a headless OpenCode server for API access. Check out the server docs for the full HTTP interface. This starts an HTTP server that provides API access to opencode functionality without the TUI interface. Set OPENCODE_SERVER_PASSWORD to enable HTTP basic auth (username defaults to opencode).','启动无界面的 OpenCode 服务器以提供 API 访问。查看服务器文档了解完整的 HTTP 接口。 此命令启动一个 HTTP 服务器，提供对 OpenCode 功能的 API 访问，无需 TUI 界面。设置 OPENCODE_SERVER_PASSWORD 可启用 HTTP 基本认证（用户名默认为 opencode）。','opencode serve',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(804,5,'delete','delete','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Delete an OpenCode session.',NULL,'opencode delete',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(805,5,'stats','stats','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Show token usage and cost statistics for your OpenCode sessions.','显示 OpenCode 会话的 Token 用量和费用统计信息。','opencode stats',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(806,5,'import','import','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Import session data from a JSON file or OpenCode share URL. You can import from a local file or an OpenCode share URL.','从 JSON 文件或 OpenCode 分享链接导入会话数据。 您可以从本地文件或 OpenCode 分享链接导入。','opencode import',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(807,5,'web','web','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Start a headless OpenCode server with a web interface. This starts an HTTP server and opens a web browser to access OpenCode through a web interface. Set OPENCODE_SERVER_PASSWORD to enable HTTP basic auth (username defaults to opencode).','启动带有 Web 界面的无界面 OpenCode 服务器。 此命令启动一个 HTTP 服务器并打开浏览器，通过 Web 界面访问 OpenCode。设置 OPENCODE_SERVER_PASSWORD 可启用 HTTP 基本认证（用户名默认为 opencode）。','opencode web',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(808,5,'acp','acp','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Start an ACP (Agent Client Protocol) server. This command starts an ACP server that communicates via stdin/stdout using nd-JSON.','启动 ACP（Agent Client Protocol）服务器。 此命令启动一个通过 stdin/stdout 使用 nd-JSON 进行通信的 ACP 服务器。','opencode acp',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(809,5,'plugin','plugin','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Install a plugin and update your config. Or use the alias.',NULL,'opencode plugin',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(810,5,'pr','pr','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Fetch and checkout a GitHub PR branch, then run OpenCode.',NULL,'opencode pr',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(811,5,'db','db','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Database tools.',NULL,'opencode db',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(812,5,'uninstall','uninstall','subcommand','Subcommand','low','official','Uninstall OpenCode and remove all related files.','卸载 OpenCode 并删除所有相关文件。','opencode uninstall',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://opencode.ai/docs/cli/','Scraped from official documentation.',NULL,'2026-06-09','2026-06-09 02:30:24','2026-06-09 02:30:24'),(813,5,'upgrade'